dlentry.dd:
Sets the schema-full-checking feature to true. This enables a validation of the
            parsed XML document against a schema (W3C XML Schema or DTD) while the document is
            parsed;

dt.uicontrol:
Enable comments and PIs in XDM model, for XSD 1.1 assertion processing (
              http://apache.org/xml/features/validation/assert-comments-and-pi-checking
              )
